        <address><p><a href="mailto:jonessl10@vmi.edu">Lt. Col. Sarah Jones</a> <br>Director of Disabilities Services <br><br>P: (540) 464-7667<br>F: (540) 464-7025 <br><br>448 Institute Hill<br>Lexington, VA&nbsp; 24450</p> <p>8:00 am-4:30 pm<br>Monday-Friday</p> </address> 
